text: Jamal Murray (born February 23, 1997) is a Canadian basketball player. He was picked 7th by the Denver Nuggets in the 2016 NBA Draft. He is tall. He wears the number 27. He played at the University of Kentucky before entering the draft. At this season's all star break, he was selected as part of the WORLD rising stars team and scored 36 points.
